criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Individuals aged ≥ 18 years, of both sexes, who agree to participate in the study,
             after reading, understanding and signing the ICF;

          -  Individuals who authorized filming during the test.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Illiterates;

          -  Participants who have already performed any other HIV self-test;

          -  Health professionals with complete higher education;

          -  Colorblind individuals.
